                   +------------------+
                   |     Walk         |
                   |------------------|
                   | + walk(): void   |
                   +------------------+
                           ^
                           |
     +----------------------+----------------------+
     |                      |                      |
+-------------+     +---------------+      +----------------+
| Walkable    |     | NoWalkable   |      | (Other Walk..) |
|-------------|     |---------------|      |----------------|
| + walk()    |     | + walk()      |      | + walk()       |
+-------------+     +---------------+      +----------------+


                   +------------------+
                   |     Talk         |
                   |------------------|
                   | + talk(): void   |
                   +------------------+
                           ^
                           |
         +-----------------+--------------------+
         |                                      |
+----------------+                     +------------------+
| Talkable       |                     | NoTalkable       |
|----------------|                     |------------------|
| + talk()       |                     | + talk()         |
+----------------+                     +------------------+


                   +------------------+
                   |      Fly         |
                   |------------------|
                   | + fly(): void    |
                   +------------------+
                           ^
                           |
         +-----------------+--------------------+
         |                                      |
+----------------+                     +------------------+
| Flyable        |                     | NoFlyable        |
|----------------|                     |------------------|
| + fly()        |                     | + fly()          |
+----------------+                     +------------------+


                        +-----------------------------+
                        |           Robot             |
                        |-----------------------------|
                        | - w : Walk                  |
                        | - t : Talk                  |
                        | - f : Fly                   |
                        |-----------------------------|
                        | + Robot(w, t, f)            |
                        | + act(): void               |
                        +-----------------------------+

ðŸ“˜ Explanation
Robot

Has three strategy fields: Walk, Talk, Fly

Uses them in act() via delegation.

Strategies

Three independent families:

Walking strategies (Walkable, NoWalkable)

Talking strategies (Talkable, NoTalkable)

Flying strategies (Flyable, NoFlyable)

Each strategy implements its interface.

Main idea of UML

Interfaces shown as abstract types

Concrete strategy classes inherit from interfaces

Robot depends on (HAS-A) strategies â†’ composition